Live dashboard showing all 20 DLs.

Imports shared logic directly from:
  process_files.py  → read_latest_file(), is_today()
  stop_tracker.py   → get_last_stop_time()

Place this file in the SAME folder as all other DL_PC files:
  dl_dashboard.py
